    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="structhaldls_1_1vx_1_1BackgroundSpikeSource_1_1Rate" kindref="compound">Rate</ref> of spike output in the Poisson spike generation mode, without effect in regular mode. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Every period, a random 8-bit number is compared to the rate value and a spike is generated if the random value is smaller-equal than the configured rate. This leads to a mean ISI of (period / (rate / 255)) and disabled spike output on rate = 0. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
